summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 to 4 inclusive, Block 11, Hillman's Lake Front Addition Division No. 1, and Block 34, Mercer's 2nd Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-209 and 17-155, respectively.
